  <div class="container">
    <div id="carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
        <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="4"></li>
        <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="5"></li>
      </ol>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img class="carousel-image d-block w-100" src="https://q-cf.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max1024x768/199/199339883.jpg" alt="First slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h5>Golden Visa Property</h5>
            <p>Want a Portuguese passport? Purchase property and join the Portuguese Golden Visa scheme. We know the agents selling these properties and can facilitate the legal and financial process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img class="carousel-image d-block w-100" src="https://q-cf.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max1024x768/199/199339883.jpg" alt="Second slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h5>Holiday Home</h5>
            <p>The Algarve has stunning weather, golden beaches, world-class golf courses and fantastic food and wine. It's the perfect destination for a holiday home.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img class="carousel-image d-block w-100" src="https://q-cf.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max1024x768/199/199339883.jpg" alt="Third slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h5>Investment Property</h5>
            <p>Property in the Algarve is cheap. It's also a popular tourist destination. Therefore renting your property will be easy and its value is likely to increase.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img class="carousel-image d-block w-100" src="https://q-cf.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max1024x768/199/199339883.jpg" alt="Fourth slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h5>Retirement Property</h5>
            <p>Superb weather, golf year-round, and wonderful food and wine - the Algarve is perfect for your retirement and a great incentive for the children and grandkids to visit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= image_tag ("SS_villa_golf_course.jpg"), class: 'carousel-image d-block w-100', alt: 'Fifth slide'%>
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h5>Golf Property</h5>
            <p>In the Algarve, properties surround some of the best courses in the world. We have excellent relations with agents who sell these properties.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img class="carousel-image d-block w-100" src="https://q-cf.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max1024x768/199/199339883.jpg" alt="Sixth slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h5>Beach Property</h5>
            <p>Enjoy sunbathing? Surfing? Or how about fresh seafood with a cold beer? The Algarve's beaches are perfect for these activities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="carousel-control-prev" data-target="#carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="carousel-control-next" data-target="#carousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

